_pdbx_database_remark.id     700 
_pdbx_database_remark.text   
;SHEET
THE SHEETS PRESENTED AS A1 AND B1 ON SHEET RECORDS BELOW
ARE ACTUALLY A SIX-STRANDED BETA-BARREL.  THIS IS
REPRESENTED BY A SEVEN-STRANDED SHEET IN WHICH THE FIRST
AND LAST STRANDS ARE IDENTICAL.
;
